= Publications 
[https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/author/37088952001 \[IEEE Xplore\]][https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=nYQ18kQAAAAJ&hl=en \[Google Scholar\]][https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Anuj-Yadav-12 \[Research Gate\]]\n

This page includes the list of my research publications, some of which are published, under review and under preparation. Please feel free to contact me or my co-authors for the extended versions of the published work or preprints of the work yet to be published.\n

*Remark:* Publications marked with asterisk *(\*)* follow aphabetical author order.

== Published
- [ *On the Commitment Capacity of Reverse Elastic Channels*]\n
*(\*)* [http://www.facweb.iitkgp.ac.in/~amitalok/index.html Amitalok J. Budkuley], Pranav Joshi, [https://manideepmamindlapally.ninja/ Manideep Mamindlapally], and *Anuj Kumar Yadav*\n
2021 IEEE International Theory Workshop (ITW), Kanazawa, Japan.

- [https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9530060 *Commitment over Compound Binary Symmetric Channels*]\n
*Anuj Kumar Yadav*, [https://manideepmamindlapally.ninja/ Manideep Mamindlapally], [http://www.facweb.iitkgp.ac.in/~amitalok/index.html Amitalok J. Budkuley], and [https://www.niser.ac.in/users/manojmishra Manoj Mishra]\n
2021 (IEEE) Twenty-seventh National Conference on Communications (NCC), Kanpur, India.

- [https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9518204  *Commitment Capacity under Cost Constraints*]\n
[https://manideepmamindlapally.ninja/ Manideep Mamindlapally], *Anuj Kumar Yadav*, [https://www.niser.ac.in/users/manojmishra Manoj Mishra], and [http://www.facweb.iitkgp.ac.in/~amitalok/index.html Amitalok J. Budkuley]\n
